title: Ep. #97 | Treasure, G(I)-DLE, TVXQ’s Yunho
description:
Eric returns for Part 1 of a long overdue solo episode and catch-up session with the Daebak fam! Tune in for a roundup of the most memorable K-pop comebacks of January 2021: 'MY TREASURE' by TREASURE, 'HWAA' by (G)I-DLE, 'Thank U' by TVXQ's Yunho, and more!"

Eric wants to hear from YOU! Fill out this survey and join Eric in creating something special for the 100th episode of Kpop Daebak: https://bit.ly/3p2Eona

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.

Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios

Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !

SUPPORT & JOIN DIVE Studios' Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/divestudios
